{"tid":2098956,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬克龍改組內閣轉右 吸前朝舊將","createTime":"2020-07-08T01:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:56:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"373535effec682677b6c59ad06889453ffc87076","tid":2098956,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200708/AJ4UEDBLWMYQTUYUPXJN3XCW6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200708%2FAJ4UEDBLWMYQTUYUPXJN3XCW6E%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivWSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=69876577\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200708%2FAJ4UEDBLWMYQTUYUPXJN3XCW6E%2F&h=c550ec98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200708/AJ4UEDBLWMYQTUYUPXJN3XCW6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍改組內閣轉右 吸前朝舊將<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J6lQtlbGou1NfL-0anOBkrw5fx4=/640x441/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TX6EHENCSCXBK447WLBLY7L3VY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ6lQtlbGou1NfL-0anOBkrw5fx4%3D%2F640x441%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTX6EHENCSCXBK447WLBLY7L3VY.jpg&h=1857ae06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n達爾馬寧（左二）取代卡斯塔納（右二）出任內政部長。<br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍為了重振經濟以挽回民望，前天進一步改組內閣，重用中間傾右的前總統薩爾科齊舊將，把預算部長達爾馬寧（Gerald Darmanin）晉升至掌管內政部，但他正在面臨強姦刑事調查，任命惹女權分子不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新內政部長捲強姦案<br />\n<br />\n達爾馬寧取代前內政部長卡斯塔納後，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n但總統府指調查不影響他的任命。<br />\n<br />\n至於司法部長，馬克龍委任無從政經驗、<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n（Roselyne Bachelot）獲委任為文化部長。外長、防長和財長就留任。<br />\n<br />\n法國《新觀察家》評論員拉菲指，今次改組顯示馬克龍不再如2017年大選般依賴中間派支持，而是着重吸引右傾選民，「他知道左翼沒其位置。我們現見到他樂於逗薩爾科齊支持者開心」。亦有分析指，馬克龍有意藉此削弱主流右派共和黨勢力，在他角逐連任時再次塑造選民要從他或極右旗手馬琳勒龐二擇其一局面。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"5d11607241aa0ae92748118243dffad8715a26fc","tid":2098956,"uid":108347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:20:32.000Z","msg":"左過龍自然會變右"},{"pid":"7c49a454ae1b1c8558a89a062aead8a5e455f801","tid":2098956,"uid":50972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:22:41.000Z","msg":"左到d人開始反咬自己<br />\n咪要轉右囉"},{"pid":"f41c00c2ce072942b532b169b857f82e0a8704d0","tid":2098956,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"其實蠢既人行極右係完全冇問題<br />\n因為即使冇本事行中庸之道、聽唔落相反意見 <br />\n行極右  最多都係保護主義  <br />\n但極左真係會搞到亡國"},{"pid":"cfcfc9bbe4c759bee1d44b37adef0855cfe5ea06","tid":2098956,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"馬克龍從來都係右 何來轉右"},{"pid":"cbccc3651dc8e68cf6ce4c05c33c6f057dbf7447","tid":2098956,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfcfc9bbe4c759bee1d44b37adef0855cfe5ea06","tid":2098956,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"馬克龍從來都係右 何來轉右"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:56:38.000Z","msg":"係連登仔眼中ibanker 都係左"}]}